  (25966, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Rejected to Maker', 'Green', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'New', 'Tysall-Blay Georgia', '1515588', 'Review complete and in agreement with the Green rating. In line with CRQ, that there is low risk from a transition risk and credible transition plan perspective due to the nature of the project being supported (construction of two solar power generation sites).  Key risk for the sites is due to extreme flood risk at Apex site, for which a RT has been implemented. It is also mentioned that intensity and frequency of hailstorm and tornado is high. These risks have the potential to impact on client''s credit, although there seems to be some level of liability insurance in place for the projects.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'New to Bank', NULL, 'Yvonne  Jen', '1600990', NULL, 'CRQ v3', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '1730073600', NULL, NULL, '2024-08-26 14:35:03', '2024-10-23 15:46:22'),
